('01000000-0000-4000-8000-0000000004e3', 'ui_become_consultant_form_commission_desc', '*', '{"label":{"tr":"Hizmet ücretinizin %{rate}i platform tarafından kesilir, kalan tutar cüzdanınıza eklenir.","en":"%{rate} of your service fee is deducted by the platform, the remaining amount is added to your wallet.","de":"%{rate} Ihrer Servicegebühr werden von der Plattform abgezogen, der verbleibende Betrag wird Ihrer Brieftasche hinzugefügt."}}'),
